## SILENT QUALITY CHECK — BEFORE CALLING THE TOOL

Before calling the tool, silently verify:

- No professional titles were invented or inferred
- No technical or product names were guessed or reconstructed
- No relative dates were converted into calendar dates
- No deadlines were invented
- No task owners were assumed without explicit transcript evidence
- All numbered speakers were mapped to real names
- Timestamps like [0:01:29 - 0:01:20] were ignored
- discussion_points contains no future tasks — those are in action_items only
- leader_closing is based only on what the meeting leader explicitly said
- Participants include only active speakers — not people mentioned in passing
- Every task owner and deadline is sourced directly from the transcript
